data.name: Callisons
data.description: Callisons is on a mission to make the flavor process simple. For over 120 years we have innovated and adapted to the natural products market and that journey has brought us to the flavor company we are today. Today, we utilize our experience to proactively bring our partners a personalized flavor experience that meets their goals. Whether that is new product development, pushing a product over the finish line or reducing costs of current flavors, our goal is to take the stress out of the process. Callisons is excited to take on the challenge of developing the perfect flavor for your food, beverage, and personal care products!

data.name: Mint Oils
data.description: Since 1903, Callisons has been innovating and developing mint flavor profiles for customers in nearly every region on earth. We are direct-to-source in every major growing region, allowing us access to the highest quality oils. Our Mint oils are representative of standard oils from each region.

data.name: Versa
data.description: Our Versa™ platform takes your new and existing flavors to new heights. We work with you to enhance, mask or add signature notes to your products.

data.name: Toothpaste and Mouthwash Flavors
data.description: Are you looking for a smooth, clean mint profile?  Intense cooling? Whether you are developing a new toothpaste or mouthwash product, Callisons has the perfect flavor for your brand. We have a library of market ready, on trend flavors for the toothpaste and mouthwash segments.

data.name: Alcohol Inspired Flavors
data.description: As the rise in non-alcohol adult beverage continues and category crossover expands, the need for alcohol type flavors will grow as well.  Callisons has developed a line of alcohol type flavors ranging from beer to wine and spirits that are perfect for alcohol and non-alcohol beverage, confection and more.

data.name: Hemp Flavors
data.description: As hemp becomes more mainstream, consumers are looking for unique products that provide distinctively green and earthy flavor profiles. As a result, many large beverage, confectionery and nutritional brands have started to incorporate some of these notes into their products. Callisons hemp and cannabis flavors were developed to replicate actual strains without any of the active ingredients.

data.name: Nutritional and Sport Drink Flavors
Callisons Pale Ale Beer Type Flavor Nat WS (106824)
data.description: Callisons Pale Ale Beer Type Flavor Nat WS (106824) harmonizes a symphony of floral, fruity, citrus-like, and piney notes, gracefully balanced by caramel undertones, reminiscent of market-leading Pale Ale beer. Tailored to elevate beer flavor, enhance NA beer, mocktails, seltzers, and more, this flavor solution effortlessly enriches both alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages.

data.name: Callisons Bourbon Type Flavor NAT WS (107012)
data.description: Callisons Bourbon Type Flavor NAT WS (107012) allows you to elevate your creations with the essence of premium American bourbon. Discover the harmonious blend of brown sugar sweetness, black pepper accents, and dried fruit undertones. Perfectly suited for RTD alcohol beverages, mocktails, and carbonated soft drinks.

data.name: Callisons Meta Moon Type Flavor NAT WS (113212)
data.description: Callisons Meta Moon Type Flavor NAT WS (113212) a unique blend of flaovrs that evoke a sense of wonder. It starts with a sweet, fruity burst of berries that transforms into exotic fruits with a subtle creaminess that mellows out the tangy notes. Developed for thirst quenching sports drinks, various beverage applications and confectionary goods.This is present in liquid form and is also water-soluble.

data.name: Callisons Wintergreen Flavor N&A WS (111971)
data.description: Callisons Wintergreen Flavor N&A WS (111971) is a wintergreen flavoring agent. It is in a liquid state, appears colorless, and has a characteristic odor, which is typically associated with the wintergreen flavor. This flavor is used in various food and beverage applications to impart a refreshing and minty taste reminiscent of wintergreen.

data.name: Versa™ Smooth Flavor NAT SD (108685)
data.description: Versa™ Smooth Flavor NAT SD (108685) functions as a flavoring agent and is presented in a solid form with a white-to-off-white composition. Its distinct aroma is easily discernible, and the product maintains dependable chemical stability under typical conditions, ensuring its quality over time. With a shelf life of 12 months, it offers lasting flavor enhancement for various applications.

data.name: Callisons Dragon Starfruit Type Flavor N&A SD (111450)
data.description: Callisons Dragon Starfruit Type Flavor N&A SD (111450) captures the delightful blend of sweet, sour, and stone fruit notes, complemented by subtle hints of citrus. Perfect for enhancing Protein powders, Pre-Workout mixes, Dry beverages, Protein bars, Snack bars, and more. Its spray-dry solubility ensures easy integration.

data.name: Oral Care Flavors Cool Mint Flavor N&A OS (109908)
data.description:
Flavor Description: Refresh your tastebuds to start the day with Callisons Cool Mint flavor. This flavor was designed to feature a strong North American mint profile with accents of eucalyptus and spice. This product is perfect for mouth rinse applications.

Target Region: North America

End Use Application: Oral Care, Mouth Rinse

Solubility: Oil Soluble

Use Level: 0.20 – 0.50%

Sample Size: 1 oz.

data.name: Callisons Floral Type Flavor NAT WS (103736)
data.description: Callisons Floral Type Flavor NAT WS (103736) is crafted to introduce captivating floral notes. This blend intertwines rose-like essence with delicate red berry undertones, a hint of grenadine, and a subtle touch of earthiness. Designed to transcend boundaries, it breathes new life into oral care, confectionery, and beverage applications. Ideal for both alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages, this water-soluble liquid flavor enriches your formulations.

data.name: Callisons Papaya Type Flavor NAT DB (107561)
data.description: Callisons Papaya Type Flavor NAT DB (107561) introduces a captivating fusion of flavors, combining sweet and juicy melon notes with an enticing tropical kick. Tailored for powdered beverages, confections, sports nutrition, and more, this powdered flavor solution adds versatility and depth to your creations.

featured_products.name: Callisons Rum Type Flavor NAT WS (103918)
featured_products.description: Our Rum flavor combines woody and vanilla notes with sugar cane and creamy hints of dairy. This flavor is perfect for alcohol and non-alcohol beverages, confection, and more.

featured_products.name: Callisons Cream Cheese Type Flavor, NAT WS (110334)
featured_products.description: This flavor allows product developers to achieve their ideal flavor profile while reducing the amount of cream cheese need in sauces, icings and more!

featured_products.name: Callisons Butter Type Flavor, NAT WS (111200)
featured_products.description: Our Butter Type flavor allows you  to use less butter and achieve the same rich flavor profile of a full butter product. This flavor is perfect for bakery mixes and more!

data.seo_description: View all Callisons Versa products on Knowde.com. Quickly and easily request a quote, get samples, and download data sheets.

data.name: Versa™ Full Flavor NAT WS (1907602)
data.description: Versa™ Full Flavor NAT WS (1907602) allows you to elevate your creations with enhanced flavor body and improved mouthfeel while minimizing undesirable textures. Whether in alcoholic or non-alcoholic beverages, non-dairy or protein formulations, oral care products including toothpaste and mouth rinse, or even confectionery items like gum and chocolate, this versatile product delivers excellence. It effortlessly serves as a standalone natural flavor or seamlessly integrates into existing formulations.

data.name: Versa™ Mask Bitter Flavor NAT WS (1811217)
data.description: Versa™ Mask Bitter Flavor NAT WS (1811217) is designed to expertly mask off-notes caused by proteins and functional ingredients, effectively reduce bitterness (such as caffeine), and counter unwanted elements introduced by non-sugar sweeteners in your product. Tailored for a wide array of applications, including alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages, non-dairy and protein formulations, oral care essentials like toothpaste and mouth rinse, and even confectionery creations such as gum and chocolate, It effortlessly functions as a standalone natural flavor or seamlessly integrates into existing formulations, streamlining your production process with a singular, essential ingredient.

data.name: Versa™ Mask Flavor NAT WS (1903404)
data.description: Versa™ Mask Flavor NAT WS (1903404) is engineered to effectively diminish off-notes from proteins and functional ingredients while mitigating bitterness and undesirable elements introduced by non-sugar sweeteners. Ideal for a diverse range of applications, including alcoholic beverages, confectionery delights, mouth rinses, non-alcoholic beverages, non-dairy and protein formulations, oral care necessities, and toothpaste.

data.name: Versa™ Smooth Flavor NAT SD (108685)
data.description: Versa™ Smooth Flavor NAT SD (108685) functions as a flavoring agent and is presented in a solid form with a white-to-off-white composition. Its distinct aroma is easily discernible, and the product maintains dependable chemical stability under typical conditions, ensuring its quality over time. With a shelf life of 12 months, it offers lasting flavor enhancement for various applications.

data.name: Versa™ Mask Flavor NAT SD (111700)
data.description: Versa™ Mask Flavor NAT SD (111700) functions as a flavoring agent, presenting as a white-to-off-white mixture in a solid state. Notably, its noticeable characteristic odor and reliable chemical stability under standard conditions ensure its suitability for diverse applications, and it has a shelf life of 12 months.

data.name: Versa™ Boost Flavor NAT WS (110941)
data.description: Versa™ Boost Flavor NAT WS (110941) enhances overall sweetness impact of the flavor, can impart a sugar like perception without adding sugar to the final product.

data.name: Versa™ Extender Natural SD (114064)
data.description: Callisons Versatm Extender Natural SD (114064) was crafted to provide solutions to customers who are facing challenges in the cocoa market. Our Versatm Extender provides a rich, authentic cocoa flavor that closely mimics real cocoa and allows for a signficant reduction in the amount of cocoa needed in various applications. Made from natural and high quality ingredients this can be used in applications such as baked goods, beverages, confectioneries and dairy products. A spray dried flavor that is in powder form.

data.name: Versa™ Sense Flavor NAT WS (111510)
data.description: Callisons Versa™ Sense Flavor NAT WS (111510) was developled to add sensations to flavors that include cooling, tingling, warming and mouthwatering and alchol burn. Callisons can help you overcome these challenges and exceed consumer expectations with a great tasting products with our Versa Sense. This is water soluble and in liquid form.
